title: Buildings across Time - An Introduction to World Architecture
description:
Buildings across Time: An Introduction to World Architecture by Marian Moffett, Michael Fazio

English | Aug 21, 2003 | ISBN: 0767405110 | 608 Pages | PDF | 123,4 MB

This heavily illustrated survey has been expanded in its second edition to provide students of both art history and of architecture with a worldwide introduction to the history of architecture
